    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《血腥符文》</strong>是一款回合制单笔画roguelike卡牌构建游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目标是根据情况使用适当的“符文”来击败所有敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/b9985569fe9445334c36e84bca285490.poster.avif?t=1763305030\" width=360 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/b9985569fe9445334c36e84bca285490.webm?t=1763305030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/b9985569fe9445334c36e84bca285490.mp4?t=1763305030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>符文</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以通过方块绘制符文，而不是简单地打破方块，从而使用符文技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/b721a303b27eb44c5297f44d08214df6.poster.avif?t=1763305030\" width=360 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/b721a303b27eb44c5297f44d08214df6.webm?t=1763305030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/b721a303b27eb44c5297f44d08214df6.mp4?t=1763305030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选择</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要考虑各种变量，例如你当前拥有的符文和下一个将要遇到的敌人，并进行有协同效果的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/9b200f5f6b23c45c562d7858e8e835ce.poster.avif?t=1763305030\" width=360 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/9b200f5f6b23c45c562d7858e8e835ce.webm?t=1763305030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/9b200f5f6b23c45c562d7858e8e835ce.mp4?t=1763305030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>商店</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中遇到的商店里，你需要考虑是立即购买更强大的符文，还是攒钱在下一个商店里购买更强的符文。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/916038f5b7942e5a014bb5972afed302.poster.avif?t=1763305030\" width=360 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/916038f5b7942e5a014bb5972afed302.webm?t=1763305030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/916038f5b7942e5a014bb5972afed302.mp4?t=1763305030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请享受游戏！</p>",
